Author: isilduuuuuuur
Text: If you've been through it before you know the hell that it's living like this. You don't deserve that. Seek help from someone you trust in your church, they should understand your reasons. Keep yourself safe first.

Author: LowCalPal
Text: It sounds like you might benefit from some guidance from your spiritual leaders.  I am sure they would discourage you from punishing yourself for God.  What parent wants their child to harm themselves for the parent's sake?
